Yes?

21
00:02:33,208 --> 00:02:34,083
An,  Hélène!

22
00:02:34,667 --> 00:02:36,083
It's nice to hear from you.

23
00:02:36,875 --> 00:02:38,500
No, I'm working.

24
00:02:38,583 --> 00:02:40,542
Yes, I'm working.

25
00:02:41,375 --> 00:02:42,792
No, I told you I'm working.

26
00:02:43,458 --> 00:02:46,000
Listen, I'll call you later.

27
00:02:46,083 --> 00:02:47,417
That's right. Goodbye.

28
00:02:47,958 --> 00:02:49,417
Talk to you later. Love you.

29
00:02:52,625 --> 00:02:53,542
Shit.

30
00:02:57,417 --> 00:02:58,750
Dammit.

31
00:02:58,833 --> 00:02:59,667
Hello?

32
00:03:00,292 --> 00:03:01,125
Yes.

33
00:03:04,250 --> 00:03:05,125
Put him through.

34
00:03:06,208 --> 00:03:07,583
Yes, put him through.

35
00:03:07,667 --> 00:03:10,708
Hello, listen, old boy,
I've helped you for the past 15 years.

36
00:03:11,417 --> 00:03:12,500
We're nearly friends.

37
00:03:12,583 --> 00:03:13,750
You're in a crisis.

38
00:03:13,833 --> 00:03:15,333
I don't want you to crumble.

39
00:03:15,417 --> 00:03:16,250
Listen to me,

40
00:03:17,167 --> 00:03:18,833
I have here in front of me

41
00:03:19,417 --> 00:03:21,958
the details of your situation

42
00:03:22,458 --> 00:03:23,333
and the results.

43
00:03:23,417 --> 00:03:25,125
-Do you want the details?
-No.

44
00:03:25,208 --> 00:03:27,042
Fine, here are the results.

45
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:29,875
I manage seven of your books.

46
00:03:29,958 --> 00:03:34,292
For the latest one,
the royalties come to 7,100 new francs.

47
00:03:34,375 --> 00:03:35,917
That's perfect. Send it to me.

48
00:03:36,833 --> 00:03:40,875
The advances I gave you come to three...

49
00:03:41,542 --> 00:03:44,000
330,000 new francs.

50
00:03:44,083 --> 00:03:45,917
The difference is

51
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:47,708
231,000 new francs.

52
00:03:47,792 --> 00:03:49,167
In other words,

53
00:03:49,250 --> 00:03:52,458
you owe me 23,100,000 old francs.

54
00:03:53,375 --> 00:03:56,958
Not only that,
but you suppose I'll pay your taxes.

55
00:03:57,042 --> 00:03:59,875
And not only that,
you suppose I'll send more money.

56
00:03:59,958 --> 00:04:01,375
There are limits, my friend.

57
00:04:02,292 --> 00:04:03,583
What do you want exactly?

58
00:04:05,250 --> 00:04:07,042
Jérôme, for three years

59
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:09,625
you haven't delivered a book.

60
00:04:09,708 --> 00:04:11,042
That's the problem.

61
00:04:11,125 --> 00:04:13,417
The problem results from another problem.

62
00:04:13,500 --> 00:04:14,792
My books are about women.

63
00:04:14,875 --> 00:04:17,375
I can't write because
I can no longer stand women.

64
00:04:17,875 --> 00:04:20,042
They've become an abomination,

65
00:04:20,875 --> 00:04:23,417
a mistake of nature.

66
00:04:24,083 --> 00:04:25,167
That's it.

67
00:04:25,250 --> 00:04:27,125
That's it! That's great.

68
00:04:27,208 --> 00:04:28,167
Write that for me.

69
00:04:28,667 --> 00:04:29,542
Go to hell.

70
00:04:52,125 --> 00:04:52,958
Yes?

71
00:04:53,042 --> 00:04:54,083
Jerome...

72
00:04:55,750 --> 00:04:56,958
I have an idea.

73
00:04:59,292 --> 00:05:00,792
What if I found you a woman...

74
00:05:03,250 --> 00:05:04,625
who doesn't weigh on you?

75
00:05:05,917 --> 00:05:07,417
Who isn't a burden?

76
00:05:09,833 --> 00:05:11,000
Who inspires you

77
00:05:11,625 --> 00:05:13,167
without tying you down?

78
00:05:13,250 --> 00:05:15,250
You just have to trust me.

79
00:05:16,208 --> 00:05:18,125
-Let me do it.
-Really?

80
00:05:18,208 --> 00:05:19,792
I'll take care of finding her,

81
00:05:19,875 --> 00:05:22,875
and you get to work if I do find her.

82
00:05:24,042 --> 00:05:25,875
So what do you say?

83
00:05:28,292 --> 00:05:30,250
"Urgently seeking secretary.

84
00:05:30,333 --> 00:05:32,833
Perfect shorthand, highly competent.

85
00:05:32,917 --> 00:05:34,042
Pretty.

86
00:05:34,125 --> 00:05:35,708
Open to all points of view.

87
00:05:35,792 --> 00:05:39,458
For short-term travel with famous author.

88
00:05:40,125 --> 00:05:41,667
High salary.

89
00:05:42,417 --> 00:05:44,792
Apply at Rene Garanciére Publishing,

90
00:05:44,875 --> 00:05:46,000
11 Servendoni Street."

91
00:06:31,042 --> 00:06:32,292
Hello, miss.

92
00:06:32,375 --> 00:06:35,417
You fit the criteria we're looking for.

93
00:06:35,500 --> 00:06:36,625
Please take a seat.

94
00:06:38,125 --> 00:06:40,708
You read the ad carefully?

95
00:06:40,792 --> 00:06:43,417
Yes, I have to travel

96
00:06:43,500 --> 00:06:46,000
as the secretary of a famous writer.

97
00:06:46,667 --> 00:06:47,625
High salary.

98
00:06:48,458 --> 00:06:49,292
Yes, um...

99
00:06:50,083 --> 00:06:51,458
There is a clause

100
00:06:52,500 --> 00:06:54,625
that may surprise you.

101
00:06:56,417 --> 00:07:00,917
It's not routine
for the publishing house to recruit

102
00:07:01,583 --> 00:07:03,458
secretaries for our authors.

103
00:07:04,667 --> 00:07:06,917
But Jerome Hervé

104
00:07:07,875 --> 00:07:09,167
is the most famous.

105
00:07:09,875 --> 00:07:10,917
We want to help him.

106
00:07:12,792 --> 00:07:15,958
He's looking for a secretary

107
00:07:17,375 --> 00:07:19,250
who is competent, which you are.

108
00:07:21,750 --> 00:07:23,792
But there's an additional...

109
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:28,125
An artist...

110
00:07:29,500 --> 00:07:33,292
needs inspiration...

111
00:07:34,458 --> 00:07:35,583
understanding...

112
00:07:37,667 --> 00:07:38,500
encouragement.

113
00:07:41,208 --> 00:07:44,000
And that is why we're asking you...

114
00:07:46,625 --> 00:07:48,375
Excuse me, miss.

115
00:07:48,958 --> 00:07:51,167
Read clause number five for yourself.

116
00:07:53,500 --> 00:07:58,000
"Said secretary agrees
to collaborate at all times,

117
00:07:58,083 --> 00:07:59,833
both day and night,

118
00:07:59,917 --> 00:08:03,083
with collaboration not limited
to a professional context."

119
00:08:03,708 --> 00:08:07,125
"She agrees to grant Jérôme Hervé
immediately upon his request

120
00:08:07,208 --> 00:08:09,292
everything a woman can grant a man."

121
00:08:09,375 --> 00:08:11,792
"Everything a woman can grant a man."

122
00:08:12,333 --> 00:08:13,875
What does that mean?

123
00:08:13,958 --> 00:08:15,792
I know full well what that means.

124
00:08:15,875 --> 00:08:18,750
-It means you take me for a whore.
-Not at all, miss.

125
00:08:19,333 --> 00:08:22,042
Understand that, like you,
I consider this clause--

126
00:08:22,125 --> 00:08:23,125
It's despicable.

127
00:08:23,208 --> 00:08:24,833
It's ridiculous.

128
00:08:24,917 --> 00:08:28,375
I'll be a slave to a man
I've never seen before.

129
00:08:28,917 --> 00:08:32,500
Do you think I'd be
a dirty old man's plaything?

130
00:08:33,083 --> 00:08:34,542
I'm not that kind of girl.

131
00:08:34,625 --> 00:08:36,083
So you decline the offer.

132
00:08:37,500 --> 00:08:39,250
No, I accept.

133
