136
00:09:42,208 --> 00:09:43,167
Hello, Marianne?

137
00:09:44,208 --> 00:09:46,125
I'm calling from the train station.

138
00:09:47,792 --> 00:09:51,208
You know leaving for work
was the only solution, darling.

139
00:09:52,583 --> 00:09:56,042
But you know I can only work
when I'm on the move.

140
00:09:56,125 --> 00:09:57,333
Traveling inspires me.

141
00:09:58,958 --> 00:09:59,875
What?

142
