01:02:46,625 --> 01:02:48,042
Because they're open.

832
01:02:48,125 --> 01:02:48,958
Yes.

833
01:02:55,250 --> 01:02:57,625
I think it's Panther Two.

834
01:02:58,167 --> 01:02:59,208
What's Panther Two?

835
01:02:59,875 --> 01:03:01,958
His boat is named Panther Two.

836
01:03:02,667 --> 01:03:03,542
Whose boat?

837
01:03:04,167 --> 01:03:05,167
Bob's boat.

838
01:03:06,208 --> 01:03:07,167
He loves me.

839
01:03:08,875 --> 01:03:10,667
He's been waiting for me for a week.

840
01:03:11,750 --> 01:03:12,625
Poor thing.

841
01:03:13,750 --> 01:03:14,583
What?

842
01:03:18,375 --> 01:03:19,417
Go on, goodbye.

843
01:03:20,917 --> 01:03:21,958
See you soon.

844
01:03:23,292 --> 01:03:24,542
We'll talk on the phone.

845
01:03:28,458 --> 01:03:30,917
Come on, don't be dumb.

846
01:03:32,167 --> 01:03:33,417
I'm not dumb.

847
01:03:34,500 --> 01:03:35,333
I'm free.

848
01:03:37,292 --> 01:03:38,708
Like you, like him.

849
01:03:39,542 --> 01:03:40,958
You don't want to marry me.

850
01:03:41,958 --> 01:03:43,042
Neither does he.

851
01:03:44,583 --> 01:03:45,667
He's like you.

852
01:03:45,917 --> 01:03:46,917
He wants to love me.

853
01:03:48,167 --> 01:03:49,625
What a good idea.

854
