-I forbid you--
-You have no right.

855
01:03:52,458 --> 01:03:53,708
Ow!

856
01:03:55,542 --> 01:03:56,792
Be sensible.

857
01:04:02,042 --> 01:04:04,083
Don't just stand there, you look foolish.

858
01:04:05,417 --> 01:04:07,292
And I don't like you to look foolish.

859
01:04:08,250 --> 01:04:09,083
My love.

860
